metadata.full_text: Professor Jane Doe teaches Calculus I in the Mathematics department. Rating: 4.7 out of 5 stars from 128 reviews. PhD in Mathematics from MIT. Research in numerical methods and pedagogy. Known for clear explanations and fair grading. Known for: clear lectures, helpful office hours, fair grading.
